### 注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=lisi&password=123456&email=lisi@qq.com


### 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=zhangsan&password=123456
### 需要携带Token访问的接口
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test/hello
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyIiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJ6aGFuZ3NhbiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTc1MTY1MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgyMzU2NDUyfQ.-GmlgG23mR8uFPwVnI223kE1qJfIpaEd_Nq2RIvdHVc

### 测试注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser&password=123456&email=test@qq.com

### 测试登录
# @no-cookie-jar
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser&password=123456

### 管理员登录（获取 token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin123

### 审核通过（替换 token 和视频 ID）
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/api/approve/1
Authorization: Bearer 这里填你登录获取的token

### 审核驳回（替换 token 和视频 ID）
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/api/reject/1?reason=内容不符合要求
Authorization: Bearer 这里填你登录获取的token